      "message": "[Major] Line 1493: This clears and persists the local tombstone before the re-invited conversation has been successfully cloned. If the clone fails or the request is invalid/unreachable, the conversation can remain resurrected locally and `isAcceptedConversation()` will then block future legitimate invites. Defer persisting `removed \u003d 0` / `erased \u003d 0` until clone success, or ensure the failure path restores the tombstone.\n```suggestion\n// Keep the tombstone until the clone succeeds, then clear removed/erased\n// in the success path that finalizes the accepted conversation.\n```",
